data.description: Welcome to your dream desert oasis! This is a  magnificent 1539 square foot, two-bedroom, two-bathroom home In Vibrant and active 55+ resort-style community of Vista Montana in Desert Hot Springs. The Chef's delight Kitchen features a large walk-in Pantry with built-ins, pullout shelving in many cupboards, abundant countertop space and under-cabinet lighting. The focal point is the expansive seating Bar Island, drawing friends and family together. The Primary Bedroom and Guest Bedroom feature Walk-in Closets and spacious Baths. With custom tile and lush carpeting throughout, along with custom window treatments, this home is move-in ready. Enjoy a wonderful outdoor experience under your covered patio with beautiful Mountain Views. Don't forget the fully finished two-vehicle garage with direct interior access and a generous laundry room with ample storage and a sink. Vista Montana boasts an enormous Clubhouse with a plethora of amenities, including a spacious Pool, multiple Spas, Sauna, shuffleboard court, outdoor BBQ areas, Fitness center, billiard room, banquet facilities, and a Dog Park.  Don't miss the chance to make this spectacular residence your own!
